To cite PROJ in publications as an evolving software project, independent of a specific software release use:

  PROJ contributors (2026). PROJ coordinate transformation software
  library. Open Source Geospatial Foundation. URL https://proj.org/.
  DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.5884394

To cite a specific PROJ release, please refer to the Zenodo landing page for PROJ for the specific version DOI of the release: 
https://zenodo.org/search?q=parent.id%3A5884394&f=allversions%3Atrue&l=list&p=1&s=10&sort=version

A BibTeX entry for LaTeX users is

.. code-block:: latex

  @Manual{,
    title = {{PROJ} coordinate transformation software library},
    author = {{PROJ contributors}},
    organization = {Open Source Geospatial Foundation},
    year = {2026},
    url = {https://proj.org/},
    doi = {10.5281/zenodo.5884394},
  }
